subSubSection.paragraph:
The species is so far reported from South Africa , Red Sea, Gulf of Aden, Persian Gulf, and Gulf of Oman ( Naderloo, 2017 ). In India , the species was recorded from Gujarat (
Gosavi et al. , 2017
) located on the west coast of India .

