subSubSection.paragraph:
This species is so far reported from East Africa, Persian Gulf, Gulf of Oman , Pakistan , India , Andaman Sea, Thailand , Hong Kong , Taiwan , Mergui Archipelago, Singapore , Australia , and New Caledonia ( Sakai, 1976 ; Davie, 1989 ; Dai and Yang, 1991 ;
